{"id": "EUVD-2023-60132", "enisaUuid": "a174a52e-98b7-31a0-876a-0327068a12fc", "description": "In the Linux kernel, the following vulnerability has been resolved:\n\ndrm/mxsfb: Disable overlay plane in mxsfb_plane_overlay_atomic_disable()\n\nWhen disabling overlay plane in mxsfb_plane_overlay_atomic_update(),\noverlay plane's framebuffer pointer is NULL.  So, dereferencing it would\ncause a kernel Oops(NULL pointer dereferencing).  Fix the issue by\ndisabling overlay plane in mxsfb_plane_overlay_atomic_disable() instead.", "datePublished": "2025-12-09T18:30:34", "dateUpdated": "2025-12-09T18:30:34", "baseScore": 0.0, "references": ["https://git.kernel.org/stable/c/8bf2d4ca521d3acb57fc1607386e749b3cc92aaf", "https://git.kernel.org/stable/c/0f98de0a11d29821d9448114178ddc1b1fe32a18", "https://git.kernel.org/stable/c/aa656d48e871a1b062e1bbf9474d8b831c35074c", "https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2023-53864"], "aliases": ["CVE-2023-53864"], "assigner": "Linux", "epss": 0.02, "enisaIdProduct": [{"id": "00e1ab57-1ca3-32ff-a020-18858f76e0e4", "product": {"name": "Linux"}, "product_version": "patch: 6.5.4"}, {"id": "2917f348-6ae8-3e81-8de6-d355611cf5f8", "product": {"name": "Linux"}, "product_version": "cb285a5348e768dbc8edfe28cc2be5ec0c7e1a33 <aa656d48e871a1b062e1bbf9474d8b831c35074c"}, {"id": "66b58018-d024-34d7-95fb-effeb585fe69", "product": {"name": "Linux"}, "product_version": "5.19"}, {"id": "6f052da2-254e-3afc-827e-222f3ebbe7fb", "product": {"name": "Linux"}, "product_version": "patch: 6.1.54"}, {"id": "b5f49529-2ec6-3c59-91c7-53f27f274b12", "product": {"name": "Linux"}, "product_version": "cb285a5348e768dbc8edfe28cc2be5ec0c7e1a33 <0f98de0a11d29821d9448114178ddc1b1fe32a18"}, {"id": "cb74fd91-2e32-305f-bb77-92565c009f23", "product": {"name": "Linux"}, "product_version": "cb285a5348e768dbc8edfe28cc2be5ec0c7e1a33 <8bf2d4ca521d3acb57fc1607386e749b3cc92aaf"}, {"id": "cdefc61a-cb6a-346d-9ea3-0d1095296dab", "product": {"name": "Linux"}, "product_version": "patch: 0"}, {"id"